data.description: Welcome to this charming 1st level unit nestled within the tranquil community of Trails at Parkfield Lake. This beautiful condo offers a comfortable and inviting living space with 1 bedrooms and 1 office space that could double as a bedroom. Upon entering, you will be greeted by the soothing ambiance created by the fresh exterior paint. The condo has been meticulously maintained, reflecting the care and attention given by its owner. The interior boasts a well-designed floor plan, maximizing both functionality and comfort. The two bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation the two bathrooms offer convenience and privacy. Sitting in the Trails at Parkfield Lake community, this unit s steps away from the community pool and residents have access to a range of amenities, including well-manicured common areas, walking trails, and Parkfield Lake Park right around the corner. Don't miss the opportunity to own this well-maintained condo, where you can enjoy the comforts of home along with the benefits of a short commute to DIA/ Downtown and much more! Contact us today to schedule a tour and experience the inviting atmosphere for yourself.
